title: UF WR Ricky Pearsall a mama boy on a mission for Gators
body_text:
Getting your Trinity Audio player ready...
Speedy Gators’ wideout Ricky Pearsall caught his mother Erin flat-footed when he arrived Sept. 9, 2000. After Erin Pearsall’s water unexpectedly broke at the family’s Arizona home, she was left to give birth to Ricky on the master bathroom floor.
